definitions.definition: Relating to, or characteristic of the penis .
Shaped like an erect human penis.
examples: My mother has a very phallic salt shaker.

definitions.definition: Relating to or exhibiting masculine or patriarchal traits, seen metaphorically as seated in the male genitalia.
